attributes.Long form description: The student disassembles a table. She first rotates it horizontally to disassemble the four legs of the furniture. Take the Allen wrench to unscrew the screws, on each side of the legs and repeat the process with the four legs of the furniture, so continue removing the shelf, and at the end the table top, put each piece on the table to finish.
